  "prompt": "Which is the best Android app locker?",
  "response": "The \"best\" Android app locker can vary based on personal preferences, features, and security needs. However, here are some popular and highly-rated app locker options available as of October 2023:\n\n1. **AppLock by DoMobile Lab**:\n   - User-friendly interface.\n   - Offers various locking methods (PIN, pattern, fingerprint).\n   - Features such as photo vault, video vault, and intruder selfies.\n\n2. **Norton App Lock**:\n   - Developed by a trusted cybersecurity company.\n   - Robust security features.\n   - Simple interface and effective locking options.\n\n3. **Keepsafe App Lock**:\n   - Combination of app locking and photo vault features.\n   - Offers a clean interface and easy-to-use functionality.\n   - Allows you to hide photos and videos as well.\n\n4. **LockIt**:\n   - Lightweight and efficient.\n   - Offers multiple locking methods and customizable settings.\n   - Includes features for hiding files and apps.\n\n5. **Smart AppLock**:\n   - Highly customizable with various locking methods.\n   - Can lock apps, settings, and emails.\n   - Provides the option to take a photo of intruders.\n\n6. **App Hider**:\n   - Combines an app locker with an app cloner.\n   - Allows you to hide apps and create duplicate apps with different settings.\n   - Good for privacy-focused users.\n\nWhen choosing an app locker, consider factors like ease of use, features, performance, and reviews. Always download apps from reputable sources like the Google Play Store to ensure security.",
